Privacy Policy
Thank you for using the Weather Assay application. This Privacy Policy is intended to explain to you how we collect, use and protect your personal information. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using our app.
The information we collect
Usage Information: When you use the Weather Assay application, we may collect information about your device, operating history, usage habits, etc., in order to improve and optimize our services.
Location Information: With your consent, we may collect your geolocation information in order to provide local weather forecasts and location services.
Other information: We may collect other information based on your use, such as your feedback, comments and suggestions on our services.
Use of information
Providing services: We use the information we collect to provide and improve Weather Assay's services, including providing you with up-to-date weather forecasts, location services, etc.
Personalized experience: We may provide you with personalized weather forecasts and recommendations based on the information we collect to meet your personal preferences and needs.
Security: We take reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use or disclosure.
Sharing and disclosure of information
We will not sell, trade or provide your personal information to any third party, except with your prior consent or as required by laws and regulations. We may share information necessary to provide services with our partners, but these partners are also bound by obligations to protect user privacy.
Data security
We take reasonable security measures to protect your personal information, including but not limited to encryption, access control and monitoring measures to prevent unauthorized access, use or disclosure.
Privacy of minors
We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of 18. If you believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will take appropriate steps to delete the information.
Updated privacy policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices and legal requirements. Any updated privacy policy will be published within the Weather Assay app and notified to you before it becomes effective.
Contact us
If you have any questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through the contact information in the app.
Last updated: [2024/04/11]
Thank you for reading Weather Assay's Privacy Policy.